<h2>Reserve books</h2>

<p>The University of Botswana Library has leapt into the 21st
century with a really excellent on-line catalogue. To access it, go
to
<br>
<a href="http://medupe.ub.bw/"><big>http://medupe.ub.bw</big></a>
<br>
(from within the UB network you can just enter "medupe"). This will
open a list of options like the following:</p>

