<p>To find reserve books, click on "By Course" and then enter
"H202". You will then be shown a list of all books on reserve for
H202. You can also search by the name of the course lecturer
("Professor" in the OPAC, which for some reason follows the American usage
in which "professor" is a general title for all academics).</p>

